perl-extutils-parsexs: perl-extutils-parsexs (XS Code to C Compiler for Perl)
perl-extutils-parsexs:
perl-extutils-parsexs: ExtUtils::ParseXS will compile XS code into C code by embedding the
perl-extutils-parsexs: constructs necessary to let C functions manipulate Perl values and
perl-extutils-parsexs: creates the glue necessary to let Perl access those functions.
perl-extutils-parsexs: The compiler uses typemaps to determine how to map C function
perl-extutils-parsexs: parameters and variables to Perl values.
perl-extutils-parsexs:
perl-extutils-parsexs: Homepage: http://search.cpan.org/dist/ExtUtils-ParseXS/
perl-extutils-parsexs:
